      <title>澳航旅客花费 10 亿积分进行忠诚度座位改造</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/qantas-flyers-splurge-1-billion-points-in-loyalty-seat-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳洲航空 (Qantas Airways Ltd.) 对其忠诚度部门进行了彻底改革，使积分兑换更加容易后，该公司的常旅客几乎立即将超过 10 亿飞行里程换成了国际航班。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/qantas-flyers-splurge-1-billion-points-in-loyalty-seat-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 02:04:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
